  Architecture:
    1. Hero — gradient, eyebrow, H1, lead, dual CTA
    2. Service Pathways — 4 advisor cards (Business Advisor, Decision Desk, The Fixer, Nucleus)
    3. Core Services Overview — what they are and who they're for
    4. Service Card Grid — full 5-card grid with pricing, detail, CTA
